{"tid":34490,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"乜依家中學學校啲思想咁撚落後","createTime":"2016-12-11T13:24:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T18:55:15.000Z","uid":4782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"415baa7900e84bc2f92cf1243e9c7d074104b04a","tid":34490,"uid":4782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:24:55.000Z","msg":"我細妹讀果間中學某科活動要影相<br />\n從佢口中得知呢啲活動應該一年都唔少次<br />\n咁差唔多都係要影幾張相 之後present  <br />\n但係又唔比用電話影 <br />\n搞到特登要走去買部相機黎做呢啲功課<br />\n次次影果十九鳩張相就算 <br />\n<br />\n其實點解唔比用電話影呢？為左啲咁嘅垃圾活動就要特登買部相機 <br />\n老老豆豆 依家啲手機影出黎嘅相唔比相機差 咁點解唔可以用手機影呢<br />\n<br />\n點解啲中學唔可以與時並進？<br />\n禁手機禁得幾耐 依家啲細佬3歲就開始玩ipad 時代唔同左架喇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：我細妹已經問同學借左幾次 佢已經唔好意思再問人借"},{"pid":"9312184a88010cec0946e1452a72acff22286a44","tid":34490,"uid":4782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:25:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f27bc59435b072bcfc3eb81fc224cdf9f3a52370","tid":34490,"uid":4782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:29:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43e06311c6fa632fd6a698005b7707550d25b7b","tid":34490,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:05:56.000Z","msg":"輕輕地留名"},{"pid":"843616e732cd49e743122771c14b77fbc5ae53a7","tid":34490,"uid":6186